dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eqi1665703544277.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eqi1665703544277.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eqi1665703544277.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"eqi1665703544277\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      XML Comment\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"eqi1665703544277__xml_comment_531600\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">XML comments are embedded within <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!-- --&gt;</code> tags.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eqi1665703544277__p_d178109e1_d178110e1_d178111e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;!--</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Comments</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">--&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eqi1665703544277__topic_d142557e1_d142558e1_d142559e1_d142560e1_d142561e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d286028e68\">\n                       \n Conversion to Struct\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eqi1665703544277__p_d178115e1_d178116e1_d178117e1\">When converted without the <code class=\"ph codeph\">/full</code> switch, comments are ignored.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eqi1665703544277__p_d178118e1_d178119e1_d178120e1\">When converted with the <code class=\"ph codeph\">/full</code> switch, an XML comment is converted to a Struct called <code class=\"ph codeph\">#comment</code>, with annotation <code class=\"ph codeph\">xmlClass</code> set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">comment</code>. The value is the comment string itself.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"eqi1665703544277__section_rfp_rg3_ddc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d286028e95\">Example: XML to Struct Conversion: Comment </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">XML code with comment</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"eqi1665703544277__pre_vqd_sg3_ddc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;p&gt;text&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;!-- my comments --&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">After conversion with <code class=\"ph codeph\">/full</code>, string returned by\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$dbgString</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"eqi1665703544277__pre_xqd_sg3_ddc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[]\n [p] = text\n [$tags]\n [xmlClass] = element\n [#comment] = mycomments\n [$tags]\n [xmlClass] = comment</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527263\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527263\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "XML Comment Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 23, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 XML Comment XML comments are embedded within <!-- --> tags. <!-- Comments --> Conversion to Struct When converted without the /full switch, comments are ignored. When converted with the /full switch, an XML comment is converted to a Struct called #comment , with annotation xmlClass set to comment . The value is the comment string itself. Example: XML to Struct Conversion: Comment XML code with comment <p>text</p> <!-- my comments --> Copy After conversion with /full , string returned by $dbgString : [] [p] = text [$tags] [xmlClass] = element [#comment] = mycomments [$tags] [xmlClass] = comment Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}